            "html_details":"<div><strong>Office timing</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><p>Thursdays 2 to 3 pm IST , or send an email to find an alternative slot. </p></div></div><div><strong>Overview</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><p>Welcome everyone to the course \"Global Film History: From the silent Era till the 1950s\".</p><p> </p><p>This course will provide you with an introduction to the history of global cinema as a visual medium, and as a social and cultural institution. The study of cinema will move chronologically from the silent period - looking at pioneers from all over the world - till the 1950s with the end of WWII. You will be introduced to cinema as a global event beyond the understanding of \"national\" approaches. This will enable you to study cinema as being a global industry from the very beginning, appreciate key filmmakers, and take note of contextualised social histories that have shaped the visual glossary of world cinema as we know it today.</p><p>Learning film history through this course, will not only help you to engage with the film culture of the past, but will also help you to understand what \"film Heritage\" is, how such histories are preserved and retold through festivals, exhibitions and archives in the present.</p><p>Thus, this course moves away from classical approaches and will encourage you to appreciate film history and become gatekeepers of the past through practical and professional methods.</p><p> </p></div></div><div><strong>Requirements (Reading List and other materials)</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><p>see list attached </p> </div></div><div><strong>Grading Rubric</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><p>the assignment is a screencast that will form 100% of their final mark<br>Throughout the course students will have formative tasks (not assessed) to prepare them for their final assignment. <br> </p> </div></div><div><strong>Attendance Policy</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><p>Absences are not encouraged. Students will be penalised for more than 2 unexcused absences. </p></div></div><div><strong>Attachment</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><table><tbody><tr><td><a style=\"color:blue\" href=\"https://ams.ashoka.edu.in/UploadFiles/Content/ProgramCourseInfo/MS-1411[MS-1411-1]/94d709ea-2704-47b1-8c3c-d80f9c60f536.pdf\" download=\"GLOBAL FILM HISTORY_BLACKBOARD.pdf\">GLOBAL FILM HISTORY_BLACKBOARD.pdf</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>",
