            "html_details":"<div><strong>Overview</strong><div class=\"cmsDescp\"><p>\u201cBhakt\u201d is a popular term in the current political landscape.This seminar works towards a deeper historical understanding of its meanings.Who is a bhakt and what is bhakti?Is it one idea or there are many bhaktis?Is there a particular literature that can be called the bhakti literature?What is the bhakti movement?Is bhakti complete and blind surrender? Or can it be an expression of dissent? To what extent is a bhakt\u2019s devotion erotic?Is bhakti a gendered phenomena?We will mostly read poetry from the Indian medieval period, including writing by Janabai and Mirabai.</p></div></div>",
